<li id="cite_note-48"><b><a href="#cite_ref-48" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.memo.ru/history/nkvd/gulag/gulag3.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.memo.ru/history/nkvd/gulag/gulag3.htm" rel="nofollow">"Система исправительно-трудовых лагерей в СССР"</a>. Memo.ru<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.memo.ru/history/nkvd/gulag/gulag3.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.memo.ru/history/nkvd/gulag/gulag3.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.memo.ru/history/nkvd/gulag/gulag3.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-01-06</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=%D0%A1%D0%B8%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B0+%D0%B8%D1%81%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%BD%D0%BE-%D1%82%D1%80%D1%83%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%8B%D1%85+%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%B3%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B9+%D0%B2+%D0%A1%D0%A1%D0%A1%D0%A0&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Memo.ru&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.memo.ru%2Fhistory%2Fnkvd%2Fgulag%2Fgulag3.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Gulag"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
